10:32.157 --> 10:34.617
-[all] Amen.
-[Grace] Uh...

10:35.201 --> 10:37.704
Arlene, how do you know these women?

10:37.787 --> 10:41.124
Oh, well, I recently joined
St. Erik Lutheran.

10:41.207 --> 10:42.876
This is my prayer group.

10:43.793 --> 10:45.628
[softly] Jesus Christ.

10:45.712 --> 10:49.132
I can't wait to hear
all about this product of yours.

10:49.215 --> 10:51.384
Okay. [stammers]

10:51.468 --> 10:52.719
Oh!

10:53.303 --> 10:55.930
Cookies! We forgot to put out the--

10:56.014 --> 10:58.058
Frankie, mind helping me with the cookies?

10:58.141 --> 11:00.268
Why, are they made of bricks?

11:01.352 --> 11:03.563
So funny. We'll be right back.

11:03.646 --> 11:04.814
