11:08.276 --> 11:09.444
[whispers] Oh, my God.

11:09.527 --> 11:12.864
Grace? Grace, did you catch
that religion thing?

11:12.947 --> 11:15.950
Since I'm not deaf like you are,
yes, I did!

11:16.034 --> 11:17.702
What are we gonna do?

11:18.203 --> 11:20.538
There's a strong rip current today.

11:20.622 --> 11:24.542
I'm going to walk right into the ocean
and be on my way to Hawaii.

11:24.626 --> 11:25.919
Let me handle it.

11:26.419 --> 11:29.923
