to talk to a bunch of Bible-thumpers

11:30.006 --> 11:31.966
about my naughty bits.

11:32.050 --> 11:34.719
No and no. I'm gonna do it.

11:35.428 --> 11:36.513
I have to do it.

11:37.263 --> 11:40.141
I've got to do it.
I hope you're getting a kick out of this.

11:40.225 --> 11:42.185
Who are you talking to?

11:52.070 --> 11:54.697
I don't think it's gonna fit.
Careful, 'cause that's glass.

11:54.781 --> 11:55.990
