12:28.648 --> 12:29.482
Whoa.

12:30.483 --> 12:31.776
[babies chuckles]

12:31.860 --> 12:32.694
What?

12:34.988 --> 12:36.614
Why are they staring at me?

12:37.949 --> 12:40.326
